obj_root_law_sections_42_e_content:
  string
  line `^1[42E. Condition for intermediary or insurance intermediary. --Without prejudice to the`
  line `provisions contained in this Act, the Authority may, by regulations made in this behalf, specify the`
  line `requirements of capital, form of business and other conditions, to act as an intermediary or an insurance`
  line intermediary.]
