obj_root_law_sections_110_f_content:
  string
  line `The provisions of`
  line `sections 3, 3A, 27B, 28B, 33, 34 clause (a) of sections 34E, 34F, 40C, 44A, 64U to 64UM (both`
  line `inclusive), 64V, 64VA, 64VB, 64VC, and 101A, 101C, 110D, 110G and 110H shall notwithstanding any`
  line `exemption granted under section 118, also apply, so far as may be, to and in relation to the general`
  line `insurance business carried on by a State Government or a Government company as defined in section`
  line `617 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956).`
