obj_root_law_sections_115:
  sectionId (18337)
  sectionNo (115)
  orderNo 244
  title `Alteration of forms.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_115_content
  footnotes `1. Subs. by Act 41 of 1999, s. 30 and the First Schedule, "Central Government" (w.e.f. 19-4-2000).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525&sectionId=18337&sectionno=115&orderno=244&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525
obj_root_law_sections_115_content:
  string
  line `The ^1[Authority] may, on the application or with the consent of an`
  line `insurer, not being a company, alter the forms contained in the Schedules as respect that insurer, for the`
  line `purpose of adapting them to the circumstances of that insurer:`
  line
  line `Provided that nothing done under this section shall exempt the insurer from supplying all information`
  line `required under this Act so far as it is possible for the insurer to do so.`
obj_root_law_sections_116:
  sectionId (18338)
  sectionNo (116)
  orderNo 245
  title `Power to exempt from certain requirements.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_116_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_116_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525&sectionId=18338&sectionno=116&orderno=245&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525
obj_root_law_sections_116_content:
  string
  line `^1[(1)] The Central Government may, by`
  line `notification in the Official Gazette, exempt any insurer constituted, incorporated or domiciled in ^2[any`
  line `country or State outside ^3[India]] ^4[from any of the provisions of this Act which may be specified in the`
  line `notification] either absolutely or subject to such conditions or modification as may be specified in the`
  line notification.
  line
  line `^5* * * * *`
  line
  line `^6[(2) This section shall apply in respect of provident societies as defined in Part III as it applies in`
  line `respect of insurers.]`
obj_root_law_sections_116_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Section 116 renumbered as sub-section (1) thereof by Act 13 of 1941, s. 63 (w.e.f. 8-4-1941).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 47 of 1950, s. 60, for "a Part B State" (w.e.f. 1-6-1950).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Act 62 of 1956, s. 2 and the Schedule, for "the States" (w.e.f. 1-11-1956).`
  line
  line `4. Subs. by Act 20 of 1940, s. 17, for certain words (w.e.f. 10-4-1940).`
  line
  line `5. The proviso omitted by Act 47 of 1950, s. 60 (w.e.f. 1-6-1950)`
  line
  line `6. Added by Act 13 of 1941, s. 63 (w.e.f. 8-4-1941).`
obj_root_law_sections_116_a:
  sectionId (18339)
  sectionNo 116A
  orderNo 246
  title `Summary of returns to be published.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_116_a_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_116_a_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525&sectionId=18339&sectionno=116A&orderno=246&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525
obj_root_law_sections_116_a_content:
  string
  line `^2[116A. Summary of returns to be published--The ^3[Central Government, before the date of`
  line `commencement of the Insurance Regulatory and Development Authority Act, 1999 (41 of 1999)] shall`
  line `every year cause to be published, in such manner as it may direct, a summary of the accounts, balancesheet, statements, abstracts and other returns under this Act or purporting to be under this Act which have`
  line `been furnished in pursuance of the provisions of this Act to the ^1[Authority] during the year preceding the`
  line `year of publication, and may append to such summary any note of the ^1[Authority] or of the ^3[Central`
  line `Government, before the date of commencement of the Insurance Regulatory and Development Authority`
  line `Act, 1999,] and any correspondence:`
  line
  line `Provided that nothing in this section shall require the publication of the ^4[statement referred to in`
  line `sub-section (2) of section 10 of the returns] referred to in sub-section (1) of section 28 ^5[or ^6[section 28A`
  line `or section 28B] or the statements referred to in sub-section (2) of section 31B or section 40B.]]`
obj_root_law_sections_116_a_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Act 41 of 1999, s. 30 and the First Schedule, "Central Government" (w.e.f. 19-4-2000).`
  line
  line `2. Ins. by s. 64, ibid. (w.e.f. 8-4-1941).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Act 41 of 1999, s. 30 and the First Schedule, for "Central Government" (w.e.f. 19-4-2000).`
  line
  line `4. Subs. by Act 6 of 1946, s. 47, for "statements" (w.e.f. 20-3-1946).`
  line
  line `5. Ins. by Act 47 of 1950, s. 61 (w.e.f. 1-9-1950).`
  line
  line `6. Subs. by Act 62 of 1968, s. 38, for "section 28A" (w.e.f. 1-6-1969).`
obj_root_law_sections_117:
  sectionId (18868)
  sectionNo (117)
  orderNo 247
  title `Saving of provisions of Indian Companies Act, 2013.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_117_content
  footnotes `1. Ins. by Act 13 of 1941, s. 65 (w.e.f. 8-4-1941).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525&sectionId=18868&sectionno=117&orderno=247&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525
obj_root_law_sections_117_content:
  string
  line `Nothing in this Act shall affect the`
  line `liability of an insurer being a company ^1[or a provident society as defined in Part III being a company] to comply with the provisions of the Indian Companies Act, 1913 (7 of 1913), in matters not otherwise`
  line `specifically provided for by this Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_118:
  sectionId (18869)
  sectionNo (118)
  orderNo 248
  title Exemptions
  content obj_root_law_sections_118_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_118_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525&sectionId=18869&sectionno=118&orderno=248&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525
obj_root_law_sections_118_content:
  string
  line `^1[118. Exemptions--Nothing in this Act shall apply--`
  line
  line `(a) to any trade union registered under the Indian Trade Unions Act, 1926 (16 of 1926); or`
  line
  line `(b) to any provident fund to which the provisions of the Provident Funds Act, 1925 (19 of 1925),`
  line `apply; or`
  line
  line `(c) if the Central Government so orders in any case, and to such extent or subject to such`
  line `conditions or modifications as may be specified in the order, to any insurance business carried on by`
  line `the Central Government or a State Government or a Government company as defined in Section`
  line `617 of the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956); or`
  line
  line `(d) if the ^2[Authority] so orders in any case, and to such extent or subject to such conditions or`
  line `modifications as may be specified in the order, to--`
  line
  line `(i) any approved superannuation fund as defined in clause (a) of section 58N of the Indian`
  line `Income Tax Act, 1922 (11 of 1922); or`
  line
  line `(ii) any fund in existence and officially recognised by the Central Government before`
  line `the 27th day of January, 1937, maintained by or on behalf of Government Servants or`
  line `Government pensioners for the mutual benefit of contributors to the fund and of their dependants;`
  line or
  line
  line `(iii) any mutual or provident insurance society composed wholly of Government servants or`
  line `of railway servants which has been exempted from any or all of the provisions of the Provident`
  line `Insurance Societies Act, 1912 (5 of 1912).]`
obj_root_law_sections_118_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Act 35 of 1957, s. 5, for section 118 (w.e.f. 1-9-1957).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 41 of 1999, s. 30 and the First Schedule, for "Controller" (w.e.f. 19-4-2000).`
obj_root_law_sections_118_a:
  sectionId (50467)
  sectionNo 118A
  orderNo 249
  title `Powers of Authority not to apply to International Financial Services Centre.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_118_a_content
  footnotes `1. Ins. by Act 50 of 2019, s. 33 and the Second Schedule (w.e.f. 1-10-2020).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525&sectionId=50467&sectionno=118A&orderno=249&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525
obj_root_law_sections_118_a_content:
  string
  line `^1[118A. Powers of Authority not to apply to International Financial Services Centre.--`
  line `Notwithstanding anything contained in any other law for the time being in force, the powers exercisable`
  line `by the Authority under this Act,--`
  line
  line `(a) shall not extend to an International Financial Services Centre set up under sub-section (1) of`
  line `section 18 of the Special Economic Zones Act, 2005 (28 of 2005);`
  line
  line `(b) shall be exercisable by the International Financial Services Centres Authority established`
  line `under sub-section (1) of section 4 of the International Financial Services Centres Authority Act, 2019,`
  line
  line `in so far as regulation of financial products, financial services and financial institutions that are permitted`
  line `in the International Financial Services Centres are concerned.]`
obj_root_law_sections_119:
  sectionId (18870)
  sectionNo (119)
  orderNo 250
  title `Inspection and supply of copies of published prospectus, etc.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_119_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_119_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525&sectionId=18870&sectionno=119&orderno=250&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525
obj_root_law_sections_119_content:
  string
  line `^2[119. Inspection and supply of copies of published prospectus, etc.--Any person may on payment`
  line `of a fee of five rupees inspect the documents filed by an insurer with the ^1[Authority] under clause (f) of`
  line `sub-section (2) of section 3, and may obtain a copy of any such document or part thereof on payment`
  line `in advance at the prescribed rate for the making of the copy.]`
obj_root_law_sections_119_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. Subs. by Act 35 of 1957, s. 5, for section 118 (w.e.f. 1-9-1957).`
  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 13 of 1941, s. 67, for section 119 (w.e.f. 8-4-1941).`
obj_root_law_sections_120:
  sectionId (18871)
  sectionNo (120)
  orderNo 251
  title `Determination of market value of securities deposited under this Act.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_120_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_120_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525&sectionId=18871&sectionno=120&orderno=251&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_33_00044_193804_1523351752525
obj_root_law_sections_120_content:
  string
  line `The market value on`
  line `the day of deposit of securities deposited in pursuance of any of the provisions of this Act with the`
  line `Reserve Bank of India shall be determined by the Reserve Bank of India whose decision shall be final.`
obj_root_law_sections_120_footnotes:
  string
  line
